{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"2919dd01-932b-4262-a6ca-06ab5be4cb58","content":"Here's how to migrate from **VSTest@3** to **Microsoft.Testing.Platform** while keeping TRX + code coverage:\n\n### 1. Update your test `.csproj`\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nThis makes each test project a self-contained executable using Microsoft.Testing.Platform.\n\n### 2. Replace `VSTest@3` with `DotNetCoreCLI@2` (or a plain `dotnet test`)\n\n```yaml\n# Before\n- task: VSTest@3\n  inputs:\n    testAssemblyVer2: '**/*Tests.dll'\n    codeCoverageEnabled: true\n\n# After\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: test\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >-\n      --configuration Release\n      --logger \"trx;LogFileName=TestResults.trx\"\n      --collect \"Code Coverage\"\n```\n\n`dotnet test` auto-detects that the projects use Microsoft.Testing.Platform and routes accordingly.\n\n### 3. Publish results & coverage\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish TRX results'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: VSTest\n    testResultsFiles: '**/TestResults.trx'\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish code coverage'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/**/*.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n> If you want Cobertura instead of the default `.coverage` format, add `--collect \"XPlat Code Coverage\"` (requires `coverlet.collector`).\n\n### Key differences from VSTest@3\n\n| Concern | VSTest@3 | Microsoft.Testing.Platform |\n|---|---|---|\n| Runner | `vstest.console.exe` | Each test project is its own exe |\n| Invocation | DLL glob pattern | `dotnet test` on `.csproj` |\n| TRX output | Built-in | `--logger trx` |\n| Coverage | `codeCoverageEnabled` | `--collect \"Code Coverage\"` |\n| Result publish | Automatic | Needs `PublishTestResults@2` |","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"72f3be78-217e-414c-a803-896246abcdac","outputTokens":596,"requestId":"BD07:4FC4C:1D4A522:20F1D3E:6A07C519"},"id":"8cbcaae8-388d-41c0-bac6-9056e237f012","timestamp":"2026-05-16T01:15:16.924Z","parentId":"0aa67554-304f-4d79-8052-5574877f9443"}
